channel.title: Player bank item ids off [317] Delta
channel.description: Hello, when I search people's banks VIA character files the item IDS are 1 higher then they actually are, for example say I have 10 mill in my bank. In the character files, it shows up as "996 10000000" versus 995. This is not the same for if I were to say equip item 1887, it would show up as 1887 in my equipment part of the character file. I'm not sure what could be causing this..

item.title: Player bank item ids off [317] Delta
